id(wsj_2348.24, parc_23.1)
sentence_form(Meridian will pay a premium of $30.5 million to assume $2 billion in deposits.)

PARC:
((pay (assume #1=($ (billion (2)) (in (deposit)) (million (30.5))))
  (Meridian) (premium (a) (of #1#))))
RASP:
((pay
  (assume #2=($ (2 (billion)) (30.5 (million)) (in (deposits)))
   #1=(Meridian))
  #1# (premium (a) (of #2#)) (to) (will)))
Matched:
  (subj pay Meridian) : (ncsubj pay Meridian _)
  (obj pay premium) : (dobj pay premium)
  (obj assume $) : (dobj assume $)
  (obj in deposit) : (dobj in deposits)
  (obj of $) : (dobj of $)
  (adjunct billion 2) (number $ billion) : (ncmod
                                            num
                                            2
                                            billion) (ncmod num $ 2)
  (adjunct million 30.5) (number $ million) : (ncmod
                                               num
                                               $
                                               30.5) (ncmod
                                                      num
                                                      30.5
                                                      million)
  (det_form premium a) : (det premium a)
  (adjunct pay assume) : (xmod to pay assume)
  (adjunct $ in) : (ncmod _ $ in)
Partial:
  (adjunct premium of) : (iobj premium of)
Remaining PARC:
  (subj assume pro)
Remaining RASP:
  (aux pay will)
  (ncsubj assume Meridian _)

  (purchase
   #3=($ #1=(in (asset) (assistance)) #1# #2=(million (473) (550)) #2#)

       #2#))

  (obj purchase $) : (dobj purchase $)
  (obj receive $) : (dobj receive $)
  (obj in asset) : (dobj in assistance)
  (obj from RTC) : (dobj from RTC)
  (obj in assistance) : (dobj in assets)
  (adjunct million 473) (number $ million) : (ncmod
                                              num
                                              473
                                              million) (ncmod num $ 473)

                                              num
                                              $
                                              550) (ncmod
                                                    num

  (conj and receive) : (conj and receive)

Remaining RASP:
